---
// Bottom-of-leaf navigation + "talk to us" CTA.
---

<div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 border-t border-ink/10 pt-6">
  <button
    type="button"
    data-collab-back
    class="text-sm text-ink/80 hover:text-red-500 underline-offset-2 hover:underline"
  >
    ← Back
  </button>
  <button
    type="button"
    data-collab-restart
    class="text-sm text-ink/80 hover:text-red-500 underline-offset-2 hover:underline"
  >
    Start over
  </button>
  <span class="ml-auto text-sm text-ink/70">
    Questions? Email
    <a
      href="mailto:hello@publicworship.life"
      class="text-red-500 underline-offset-2 hover:underline"
    >
      hello@publicworship.life
    </a>
  </span>
</div>
